r possesses the following oracle property in variable\nselection: When $f$ depends on only a subset $S$ of variables, the $\\ell_2$\nrisk of the block estimator automatically achieves up to a poly-logarithmic\nfactor the minimax rate based on the oracular knowledge of $S$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Dec 2018 04:58:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jan 2020 03:39:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-13"}
