d data misfit.\nThe tested GN inversion was unable to recover a solution with the appropriate\ndata misfit. Our results suggest that deterministic inversion performance\nstrongly depends on the inversion approach, starting model, true reference\nmodel, number of iterations and noise realization. In contrast,\ncomputationally-expensive probabilistic global optimization always finds an\nappropriate solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Dec 2018 14:22:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 23:09:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 May 2019 14:14:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 May 2019 09:09:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
